{
  "id": "adv_main_04_07_03",
  "title": "星空編1章33話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_dangerous-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_03-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "すみません、お待たせしました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kyi",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kyi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_03-kyi001.m4a",
      "text": "いや、構わない\n私も今来たところだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.8333333175,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 8.0333330632
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_03-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "……ところで、ここにある大量のペットボトルは一体？\nもしかして、朝倉さんが全部飲むんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kyi",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kyi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_03-kyi002.m4a",
      "text": "そんな訳ないだろう。適当に選びたまえ\n……好みが分からないから、ひと通り用意しただけだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.1333334447
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_03-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "え……あ、そう……でしたか\nありがとうございます……いただきます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kyi",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kyi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_03-kyi003.m4a",
      "text": "それで、話というのは？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.166666778,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.966666778
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_03-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "あ……その……\nこ……ここって本当に、ひと気がないんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kyi",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kyi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_03-kyi004.m4a",
      "text": "女将さんに一言申しつけて人払いをしてある\nしばらくは、誰かに聞かれることもないだろう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.5666657608
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_03-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "そうですか……。えっと、今日の旅行は、その……\nゆ、優が暴走しちゃったの、凄く意外で――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kyi",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kyi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_03-kyi005.m4a",
      "text": "そんな話をするために、わざわざ呼び出したのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.7999985856,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_contact-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 60.9999985856
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.9999985856
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_03-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "……っ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.9999985856,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kyi",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kyi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_03-kyi006.m4a",
      "text": "私は、君が本当に話したいことを聞くために来た\n遠慮する必要はない、話しなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.3666754247
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_03-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "……分からないんです、私\n何を話したいのかも、何を話せばいいのかも、全然……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 83.2666754247
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_03-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "今日の旅行、どりきゅんのお二人は\n私達のブレイクスルーになると言っていました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_03-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "けど本当に？ って疑問と、焦りと不安が\nどうしてもずっと拭いきれなくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.0666651408,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 97.8000057062
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_03-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "でもこの対話の先に、掴める何かがあるかもしれない\nだから必死に考えてみたんです。けど……結局……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.9333302815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kyi",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kyi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_03-kyi007.m4a",
      "text": "そうか……ならば、こちらの聞きたいことから話そうか\nあの日、君がバンプロへ入所した本当の理由はなんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.4000015258,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanpresident-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanpresident-00-noon",
      "startTime": 121.0166733901
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanpresident-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanpresident-00-noon",
      "startTime": 121.0166733901
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 121.2666733901
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_03-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "それは……\n……あなたが、いたからでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.5666681925,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanpresident-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanpresident-00-noon",
      "startTime": 124.5666681925
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_03-rui012.m4a",
      "text": "最初は偶然でした。バンプロに入所したいと話したら\nそこの社長が父であるあなただと、母に聞かされて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.5666681925,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanpresident-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanpresident-00-noon",
      "startTime": 137.8333298842
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanpresident-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanpresident-00-noon",
      "startTime": 143.1000015258
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_03-rui013.m4a",
      "text": "私は、振り向かせたかったんです。あなたを……\n私と母を捨てた、あなたのことを",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.1000015258,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 148.5499965508
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 148.7999965508
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_03-rui014.m4a",
      "text": "だから、あなたが絶対に無視出来ないような\nアイドルになってやるって、研鑽を重ね続けた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.1333348591,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 157.8333298842
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_03-rui015.m4a",
      "text": "あなたが夢中になっていた長瀬麻奈を超えれば\nそれは叶うはずだからって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.2000015258,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 165.0333298842
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 165.0333298842
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kyi",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kyi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_03-kyi008.m4a",
      "text": "……そうか\nやはり、そういうことだったんだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.9000015258,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 170.4666632175
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 173.4333348591
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_07_03-rui016.m4a",
      "text": "……っ。その言い方……\nやっぱり、全部気付いていたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 173.4333348591,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kyi",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kyi.png",
